****************

 I'm 19 years of age, and I have been using computers (Amiga/PC) since 1988.
Since then I have studied electronics/computers for tree years, and later
this year (1993/early 1994) I will join the army (I didn't volunteer!!).

I've written programs in BASIC, PASCAL (Amiga & PC) and Assembly laguage
until now. But when I bough my A4000, C seemed to be the "natural" choice.

Solitaire is one of my "first" C programs, and because of that it's
not perfect. But one of my highest goals are to write system friendly
